      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom-fresh condition. Every aspect of this car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a mirror-like finish on the original factory paint with absolutely zero rock chips or swirl marks. Inside, the leather remains supple and uncreased, still retaining that distinct new-car scent, while the dashboard and trim are free of even the slightest blemish. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; it has been serviced exclusively at the dealership with a complete, documented history included. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the ride is as tight and silent as the day it was delivered. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this collector-grade example requires no apologies and no extra work\u2014it is ready for the road or the show floor.",
